4361687615055389, \"text\": \"Christian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If the IOC's transgender torch bearers were not enough, then what about the fact that they have now made a sport out of men battering women?\", \"from\": 335, \"to\": 475, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 342, \"end\": 345, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.9399090251794172e-15, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pope Francis may be silent in the face of this Chrysophobia outrage, but Cardinal Burke, Bishop Strickland, and the heir to the French throne are speaking out.\", \"from\": 477, \"to\": 636, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 477, \"end\": 489, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pope_Francis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pope Francis\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19546\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pope_Francis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pope_Francis\"}, {\"begin\": 550, \"end\": 564, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raymond_Leo_Burke\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cardinal Burke\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raymond_Leo_Burke\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raymond_Leo_Burke\"}, {\"begin\": 605, \"end\": 611, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9990898124535813, \"rank\": 0.0006762420484249221, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You will not believe what Louis de Bourbon said about the woke haters who are currently running his beloved France\\u2026into the ground.\", \"from\": 637, \"to\": 768, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 663, \"end\": 679, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louis_Alphonse_de_Bourbon\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.65056779279199e-19, \"text\": \"Louis de Bourbon\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louis_Alphonse_de_Bourbon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louis_Alphonse_de_Bourbon\"}, {\"begin\": 745, \"end\": 751, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kingdom_of_France\", \"score\": 0.9647704198382625, \"rank\": 0.03648961125320163, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kingdom_of_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kingdom_of_France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mover over Idiocracy - Kackling Kammy may well be your next president.\", \"from\": 770, \"to\": 840, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 781, \"end\": 790, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Idiocracy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Idiocracy\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q11424\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Idiocracy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Idiocracy\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Impossible?\", \"from\": 841, \"to\": 852, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Yes, that's what they said about Basement Biden the last time around.\", \"from\": 853, \"to\": 922, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 895, \"end\": 900, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_Biden\", \"score\": 0.9999992709365799, \"rank\": 7.290620596343176e-07, \"text\": \"Biden\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_Biden\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_Biden\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She can easily win - all she has to do is promise to kill more babies than the last jackass.\", \"from\": 923, \